{"tid":881521,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"俾你返到人生某個時間點重新開波經歷所有野，你制唔制？","createTime":"2018-10-29T13:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T05:54:20.000Z","uid":33898,"like":81,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b67946d9bb653b5d0560eca6f6fc4f7de81a1c16","tid":881521,"uid":33898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:26:35.000Z","msg":"可以任意係出生後任何一個時間點開始，然後一切都會以當時既背景設定重新運行。現有記憶會被永遠清洗唔會被帶返過去。所有已知既所有客觀事實都唔會改變，例如你選擇返到中一開學呢個位開始，你就會變返你係當時既形態同擁有同當時一樣既思維，你一開始既老師同學都會係同一班人，會係某一日自然死既人依然都會係果日死，六合彩每一期既結果都唔會改變。重啟後唯一既不確定性只有你既行動，例如你前日食24蚊餐但係重啟之後你可能會選擇去食鋒味漢堡。而當重啟後時間再次推進到依家呢個時間點既時候，一切都依然會以重啟後既方式繼續運作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 制，重新嚟過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔制，依家咁就好"},{"pid":"50ccff0977b1d9be2339186bc71b7401169207fc","tid":881521,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:31:51.000Z","msg":"睇左relife?"},{"pid":"b4956fc5586283a49a801657e1b412d03287ca55","tid":881521,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:33:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c305c4eab94a59207d3c57e42864a59ad9dfed9c","tid":881521,"uid":10680,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:34:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b47f3e1b156d3dc2a8af823d2ea2f8e943c71819","tid":881521,"uid":168629,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:43:48.000Z","msg":"唔係而家幾好而唔制，係重啟左又無記憶用返果時思維好似無嘜意義。<br />\n例如好老土既example, 如果比我回到過去我會努力讀書。但重啟返去我都係懶西一個無呢個思維想法，一切用返果時既我去運行，咁重啟好似無嘜思義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55dac0d49c21816974b05f4d3db3723c1d113c89","tid":881521,"uid":9125,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:45:47.000Z","msg":"同重播冇分別,重要唔知重播緊,on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97338e10d5f73ccd2c2bd473c473d968a1a0c3e","tid":881521,"uid":34090,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:47:40.000Z","msg":"冇記憶就冇意思 只係重新黎一次 仲要你唔知道重黎過一次 結果好似咩都冇發生過咁"},{"pid":"e7796b384d79d7133a5d514ac77a083aea1727f1","tid":881521,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:00:14.000Z","msg":"根據呢個設定，即係重新做多次同樣嘅嘢，有咩為？唔制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c52abb6beea9255e5c5860c99e816bf2e31a32","tid":881521,"uid":117754,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:03:33.000Z","msg":"有咩慘得過食屎？"},{"pid":"793c29fe2d8e213afacd358034bbe3cfd371b7a9","tid":881521,"uid":59906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:07:16.000Z","msg":"冇記憶就冇意義<br />\n假設所有條件相同<br />\n結果都會係一樣<br />\n唔會有任何轉變<br />\n命題本身就fail左"},{"pid":"0252b166a9c47852347854eb4acf6255b84652f0","tid":881521,"uid":117082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a6c52abb6beea9255e5c5860c99e816bf2e31a32","tid":881521,"uid":117754,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:03:33.000Z","msg":"有咩慘得過食屎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:08:07.000Z","msg":"睇呢個post"},{"pid":"63290c544d7751a3144ed13f24b39217151c806d","tid":881521,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"唔要<br />\n<br />\n咁辛苦先捱過咗, 又要我再經歷多次, 不了"},{"pid":"2d696302a8bb364296d8191ae41f0cb79fb309bf","tid":881521,"uid":180851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0252b166a9c47852347854eb4acf6255b84652f0","tid":881521,"uid":117082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a6c52abb6beea9255e5c5860c99e816bf2e31a32","tid":881521,"uid":117754,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:03:33.000Z","msg":"有咩慘得過食屎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:08:07.000Z","msg":"睇呢個post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:16:13.000Z","msg":"係食屎twice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78bc62f52bb166d83a4c76362